<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bạsmk yạ rb ndʿw</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- biạs̊mika yā rabũ nad̊ʿū
 ạảyũhā ạlạib̊nu ạl̊ḥabīb̊
 ạản̊ta lilạảf̊rāḥi nab̊ʿu
 ạản̊ta ṣakẖ̊runā ạl̊ʿajīb̊

[V2]
 2- jī̊̉ta min̊ ḥiḍ̊ni ạảbīka
 ʿan̊hu qad̊ kẖabãr̊tanā
 ḥubũhu qad̊ bāna fīka
 qaṣ̊dahu ʿarãf̊tanā

[V3]
 3- wamaḍaẙta lilṣãlībi
 kaẙ tahab̊ līa ạl̊qabūl̊
 bifidāyỉka ạl̊ʿajībi
 lī ại̹lay̱ ạl̊ʿulạa ạldũkẖūl̊

[V4]
 4- ạảyũhā ạl̊fādī ạl̊ʿaẓīmu
 damuka yuṭahĩru
 fīka qad̊ fāza ạlạảtẖīmu
 bibiriⁿ̃ yubarĩru

[V5]
 5- ạản̊ta biruⁿ̃ lī wasit̊ruⁿ
 min̊ kulĩ kẖiz̊yiⁿ maʿīb̊
 qad̊ maḥaẘta kulã ại̹tẖ̊mī
 yā laḥubĩka ạl̊ʿajīb̊

[V6]
 6- laẙsa lī ʿan̊ka ạn̊fiṣāluⁿ
 yā ḥabībī wālnãṣīb̊
 lạa walạa ʿan̊ka ạn̊tiqāluⁿ
 falaka ạl̊ḥam̊du yaṭīb̊</lyrics>
</song>